# Project Rules

To get an idea about the project read [README.md](README.md).

This document contains **AI-specific and meta rules only**.

## Claude Agents

Make sure to configure yourself with the .claude/ folder in the project, most important .claude/settings.json and .claude/settings.local.json

## Canonical Project Rules

All coding, architecture, testing, and workflow rules are defined in [CONTRIBUTING.md](CONTRIBUTING.md), recursively read all referenced docs.

## Enforcement

AI assistants must follow all rules defined in CONTRIBUTING.md, everything else is discussable.
Do not restate or reinterpret project rules locally.

Any conflict is resolved in favor of CONTRIBUTING.md.
